      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at VAD operating speeds and flow rates; blood analogue properties justified.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry but at lower rotational speeds than the VAD COU envelope. Operating condition overlap is approximately 60%. Relevance gap is significant at MRL 5."
