      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model form uncertainty; alternative model forms compared against experimental data.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for both the turbulence closure (SST k-ω) and the power-law hemolysis model has not been systematically assessed. No alternative model form comparison has been conducted. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
